Download attachment(s)

Usage: mxr attachments download [OPTIONS] <MESSAGE_ID> [INDEX]

Arguments:
  <MESSAGE_ID>
  [INDEX]       Attachment index (1-based, omit for all)

Options:
      --account <ACCOUNT>
      --dir <DIR>          Output directory
  -h, --help               Print help
